NAME
  halfpages - splits every image in a folder in half vertically
SYNOPSIS
  halfpages
DESCRIPTION
  halfpages takes every png image in the current folder and splits it
  in half vertically. This can be useful for takes pages from a PDF 
  where both sides of the page are on the same 'sheet' and creating
  a result PDF where they are separate.
  Conversion is performed using ImageMagick(1)'s convert(1) utility.
  The output files are placed into a 'out' subfolder, 
  which is created if needed.
SEE ALSO
  ImageMagick(1), convert(1)
AUTHOR
  Ryan Armstrong <software@zerker.ca>
